A_{1}\left( d \right)&=&55.583d^{2}-119.283d+150.409\\
{\nonumber} \sigma&=&68.410,
\end{eqnarray}
agreeing qualitatively with the similar treatment made for the ground bands of even-even nuclei in Ref. \cite{Del15}.

